OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FA judge has warned of the dangers of
OL,8,Funregulated sperm donation after a
OL,9,Fcouple's "nightmare" court case with a
OL,10,Fman who claims to have fathered 180
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FRobert Charles Albon advertises his
OL,14,Fservices on social media under the
OL,15,Fname "Joe Donor." He claims to have
OL,16,Ffathered more than 180 children in
OL,17,Fcountries as far away as Argentina and
OL,18,FAustralia.
