OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FOne couple who used his services said
OL,8,Fthe situation turned into a
OL,9,F"nightmare" after he took them to
OL,10,Fcourt demanding parental rights and to
OL,11,Fbe named on the birth certificate.
OL,13,FRejecting his demands, the judge took
OL,14,Fthe unusual step of naming Albon, who
OL,15,Fwas born in the United States but now
OL,16,Flives in the North East of England.
