OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FHis Honour Judge Jonathan Furness KC,
OL,8,Fsitting as a deputy high court judge,
OL,9,Fsaid it was in the "public interest"
OL,10,Ffor Albon to be named, so "vulnerable
OL,11,Fwomen who are interested in such
OL,12,Fservices should fully understand the
OL,13,Frisks of becoming involved with him".
OL,15,FThe court heard the same-sex couple
OL,16,Fintended Albon to have no future
OL,17,Finvolvement until the child asked
OL,18,Fabout their paternity and expressed a
OL,19,Fdesire to see him.
