OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FIn his written report, Mr Furness said
OL,8,FAlbon's advertisements suggested he
OL,9,Fwould "leave it up to the mother as to
OL,10,Fwhether there should be any contact"
OL,11,Fand had only seen the child once for a
OL,12,Fphoto, in a meeting that lasted no
OL,13,Fmore than 10 minutes.
OL,15,FMr Furness also rejected Albon's
OL,16,Fallegations that he and the biological
OL,17,Fmother had secretly had sex in the
OL,18,Fback of a car, with the baby actually
OL,19,Fconceived by syringe injection.
