OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FThe court also heard the proceedings
OL,8,Fhad resulted in a breakdown in the
OL,9,Fcouple's relationship but both mothers
OL,10,Fcontinued wanting to be parents to the
OL,11,Fchild, with care split between them.
OL,13,FAlbon had asked for the non-biological
OL,14,Fmother to instead be called "aunty",
OL,15,Fdespite her having been present at the
OL,16,Fbirth and being called "mother" by the
OL,17,Fchild.
OL,19,FThe judge also heard the court case
OL,20,Fhad caused the biological mother's
OL,21,Fmental health to suffer.
