OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FHe said Albon's actions were "wrapped
OL,8,Fup in a veneer of seeking to protect
OL,9,Fthe welfare of (the child)" but in
OL,10,Freality, he was a man who "seeks to
OL,11,Fcontrol".
OL,13,F"Women and children appear to be
OL,14,Falmost a commodity to him as he sets
OL,15,Fabout increasing the number of his
OL,16,Fchildren around the globe ` China,
OL,17,FUSA, Argentina, Australia and UK to
OL,18,Fname just some of the countries where
OL,19,Fhe has fathered children," he said.
