OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FThe case, which was first reported by
OL,8,Fthe BBC, was heard at Cardiff Family
OL,9,FCourt in late 2023, when Albon was 52,
OL,10,Fbut the written judgement has only
OL,11,Frecently been published.
OL,13,FThe judge suggested the donor had
OL,14,Fstarted the court proceedings to
OL,15,Fsupport his immigration position to
OL,16,Fstay in the UK ` something Albon
OL,17,Fdenied ` but he carried on pursuing
OL,18,Fthe case even after that matter was
OL,19,Fsettled.
