OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FMr Furness said: "Although it is right
OL,8,Fto acknowledge that he has continued
OL,9,Fto pursue his applications even after
OL,10,Fhis immigration position had been
OL,11,Fsettled I am not convinced that that
OL,12,Fis because of a genuine interest in
OL,13,Fthe child."
OL,15,FInstead, the judge said he suggested
OL,16,Fit was a "means to control" or
OL,17,F"punish" the mothers.
