OL,3,CJudge warns of sperm donor who claims
OL,4,Cto have fathered more than '180
OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FJudge said this and a similar case
OL,8,F"highlights the need for women to
OL,9,Funderstand the risks which they expose
OL,10,Fthemselves to in approaching
OL,11,Funlicensed, unregulated, and
OL,12,Funofficial sperm donors".
OL,14,FBoth women and the guardian supported
OL,15,Fnaming Albon, with the non-biological
OL,16,Fmother saying the world needs to know
OL,17,Fthe risks associated with unregulated
OL,18,Fsperm donation, calling the two-year
OL,19,Fcourt battle a "nightmare" and a
OL,20,F"horror story".
