OL,5,Cchildren'
OL,7,FNeither woman opposed one annual email
OL,8,For card each year to the child from
OL,9,FAlbon under so-called "letterbox
OL,10,Fcontact", with the items kept for when
OL,11,Fthe child is able to understand them.
OL,13,FAlbon advertises his unregulated
OL,14,Fservices on social media, with his
OL,15,FFacebook page saying he can "help with
OL,16,Fa baby anywhere in the UK".
OL,18,FAt licenced premises, men are allowed
OL,19,Fto father children with no more than
OL,20,F10 families but there is no legal
OL,21,Flimit on unofficial services.
